  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b6198cdbfb3ab42799698812d172dc50, type: 3}
  m_Name: Heimdall_Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ISUGameDev.SpearGame.Dialogue.Dialogue
  dialogueStrings:
  - Welcome Valkyrie.
  - I wish I could give you a warmer welcome, but these are troubling times.
  - I am Heimdall and this here is Ratatoskr.
  - Well met.
  - Well met to you as well, my lady.
  - I will be direct. Ragnarok is upon us.
  - The Gods have slain the frost giant Ymir and Loki seeks to free and recruit his
    brother, Surtr and harness his rage.
  - I fear the 9 realms are at stake if Loki is successful.
  - You may be our last hope.
  - It is my one duty to protect this world, my friend. It would be an honor to fight.
    Tell me what I need to do.
  - I expected no less from you.
  - The plan is a simple one. Seek out and vanquish Loki and his allies.
  - I will first send you to Midgard. It has fallen to chaos ever since this war
    has sparked up.
  - Once you have arrived, maybe you can find more information about where Loki may
    be lurking.
  - I have high hopes that you will succeed. If you have any doubts, have no fear,
    Valkyrie, for you will not be alone.
  - Ratatoskr and I will be at your side ready to transport you with the Bifrost
    to wherever you must go.
  - Call and we will answer, my lady.
  - I wish you luck.
  characterIcon: {fileID: 0}
  characterName: Heimdall & Ratatoskr
